        Select tracks where you offer coaching. Riders will see you on these locations.
      </p>

      {allTracks.length > 0 && (
        <input
          type="search"
          value={trackSearch}
          onChange={(e) => onTrackSearchChange(e.target.value)}
          placeholder="Search by track name..."
